levels.description: For [Defender] Operators only; ATK and Max HP <@ba.vup>+100%</>, Block <@ba.vup>+1</>; when there are at least <@ba.vup>3</> [Defender] Operators on the field, all [Defender] Operators gain this effect; when there are at least <@ba.vup>6</> [Defender] Operators on the field, the effect increases to <@ba.vup>2.5</>x and grants an additional <@ba.vup>+1</> Block
